-- Bertrandt Earnings Won’t Slow This Year, Boersen Zeitung Reports
-- B y   N i c h o l a s   C o m f o r t
-- 2012-06-01T17:36:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-01/bertrandt-earnings-won-t-slow-this-year-boersen-zeitung-reports.html
Bertrandt AG (BDT) ’s earnings growth won’t
slow in the second half of the year, Boersen-Zeitung reported,
citing Dietmar Bichler, the German company’s chief executive
officer, as saying in an interview.  The supplier of services to the automotive sector wants to
finance growth with its own funds and is focusing on  Germany ,
the newspaper said in an e-mailed summary of an article to be
published tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
